.SH NAME
open-inspector-config - Inspect a Terraform/OpenTofu module directory


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBopen-inspector config  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
config parses every .tf, .tf.json, .tofu, and .tofu.json file
in  (non-recursive) and prints either a human-readable summary
table or a versioned JSON envelope.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--fail-on\fP="error"
	exit nonzero if a diagnostic with this severity is present: error|warning|never

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for config

.PP
\fB--json\fP[=false]
	emit machine-readable JSON instead of a human table


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--log-level\fP="info"
	log-level: debug|info|warn|error

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	disable colored output

.PP
\fB--quiet\fP[=false]
	suppress informational log output


